      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Alex Morozov</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:139px;\"><a href=\"/IOCSC_2010\" title=\"IOCSC 2010\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/83/AlexMorozov.JPG\" width=\"137\" height=\"179\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:AlexMorozov.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alex Morozov <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Aleksey (Alexey, Alex) Morozov</b>,<br />\nan Ukrainian chess programmer and author of the chess program <a href=\"/Booot\" title=\"Booot\">Booot</a>. Alex reported on the <a href=\"/CCCCISC_2008\" title=\"CCCCISC 2008\">1st Computer Chess Championship of CIS Countries</a> 2008 in Moscow <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and is recently quite active in playing over the board as well as online tournaments with Booot. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_Morozov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alex Morozov</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>The 1st Computer Chess Championship of CIS Countries</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#31_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 31 No. 2</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_Morozov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61758\">Booot 6.1 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alex Morozov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 18, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63934\">Booot 6.2 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alex Morozov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 08, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67849\">Booot 6.3 Release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alex Morozov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 29, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77243\">Booot progress</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alex Morozov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_Morozov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=792\">Alex Morozov's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sdchess.ru/Booot.htm\">Booot by Алексей Морозов, Украина</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alex_Morozov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/IOCSC_2010\" title=\"IOCSC 2010\">1st Italian Open Computer Chess Cup</a>, November 14-15, 2010, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.giocandoconire.it/\">Giocando con i Re - Home</a> (Italian)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alex Morozov</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>The 1st Computer Chess Championship of CIS Countries</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#31_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 31 No. 2</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228235903\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 47/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 102/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion